Package uk.co.caprica.vlcj.player

Class MediaMetaData

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.caprica.vlcj.player.MediaMetaData
  • public final class MediaMetaData
extends Object
    Meta data value object.

    This is a "detached" value object.

    Compare this with MediaMeta and DefaultMediaMeta which are used to both read and write meta data and are linked "live" with the native media handle.
